RpmInfo
RpmInfo


 &reftitle.intro;


  This extension enables you to retrieve information from RPM files
  or from the installed RPMs database.



  It also provides a rpm stream wrapper to retrieve RPM content
  (since version 1.0.0 with librpm  >=  4.13).



